headline: Testing & Diagnostics Services Stocks Q4 Recap: Benchmarking Quest (NYSE:DGX)
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Quest (NYSE:DGX) and the best and worst performers in the testing & diagnostics services industry.
